&lt;h3&gt;Daily rotate a busy app&amp;rsquo;s logs&lt;span class="hx:absolute hx:-mt-20" id="daily-rotate-a-busy-apps-logs"&gt;&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;a href="#daily-rotate-a-busy-apps-logs" class="subheading-anchor" aria-label="Permalink for this section"&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;p&gt;Rotate logs for a busy app daily, but only if there&amp;rsquo;s at least 50MB of data in the log:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class="hextra-code-block hx:relative hx:mt-6 hx:first:mt-0 hx:group/code"&gt;
&lt;div&gt;&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma"&gt;&lt;code class="language-plaintext" data-lang="plaintext"&gt;&lt;span class="line"&gt;&lt;span class="cl"&gt;/var/log/myapp.log {
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="line"&gt;&lt;span class="cl"&gt; daily
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="line"&gt;&lt;span class="cl"&gt; minsize 50M
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="line"&gt;&lt;span class="cl"&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="line"&gt;&lt;span class="cl"&gt; rotate 14
